{"tid":1825005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人權觀察年度報告批港警用過度武力　斥中國威脅國際人權體系","createTime":"2020-01-15T02:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T03:09:08.000Z","uid":48973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1a75c65e2c2194f080335d9a6330c7e2f7f833","tid":1825005,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200115/s00001/84e895d9d26f0ec9afb95d1e7da04b11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200115%2Fs00001%2F84e895d9d26f0ec9afb95d1e7da04b11.jpg&h=730b3908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周日在香港被拒入境的人權觀察組織（Human Rights Watch）執行長羅斯（Kenneth Roth），周二（14日）在紐約聯合國總部發表2020年世界人權報告，批評中國威脅國際人權體系，又指摘香港警察對示威者使用過度武力。<br />\n<br />\n這份長652頁的報告，封面用了香港示威者集會的相片，當中批評香港警察對示威者使用過度用武力，增加對集會自由的限制，批評特首林鄭月娥拒絕成立獨立調查委員會調查警暴。<br />\n<br />\n報告譴責中國對待新疆維吾爾族人的行為，並稱中國試圖將其審查延伸到海外。羅斯在報告中指出，中國不但在國內「建構奧威爾式高科技監控國家」及精密的互聯網內容審查系統，在海外中國亦利用其日益增長的經濟實力打擊批評者，對全球維護人權體系發動自該體系20世紀中期形成以來最強烈的攻擊。「如果任其橫行，北京的行動可能帶我們走向一個反烏托邦，屆時人人難逃中國審查，孱弱的國際人權體系不能再制衡政府的壓迫」。報告又批評美國和歐盟等西方國家，未能挺身指摘中國，呼籲各國抗衡。<br />\n<br />\n在新聞發布會尾段，中國駐聯合國代表團人員邢繼盛不滿，向記者表示中國完全不接受人權觀察的「偏頗和捏造」的年度報告。他重申，香港是中國一部份， 又指從羅斯的言論便知道他被禁入境香港的原因。<br />\n（人權觀察網站/路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200115/s00001/1579053213592/%e4%ba%ba%e6%ac%8a%e8%a7%80%e5%af%9f%e5%b9%b4%e5%ba%a6%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a%e6%89%b9%e6%b8%af%e8%ad%a6%e7%94%a8%e9%81%8e%e5%ba%a6%e6%ad%a6%e5%8a%9b-%e6%96%a5%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%a8%81%e8%84%85%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e4%ba%ba%e6%ac%8a%e9%ab%94%e7%b3%bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200115%2Fs00001%2F1579053213592%2F%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25ac%258a%25e8%25a7%2580%25e5%25af%259f%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%2591%258a%25e6%2589%25b9%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%2594%25a8%25e9%2581%258e%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%258a%259b-%25e6%2596%25a5%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2584%2585%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25ac%258a%25e9%25ab%2594%25e7%25b3%25bb&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=9a5ebd66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200115%2Fs00001%2F1579053213592%2F%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25ac%258a%25e8%25a7%2580%25e5%25af%259f%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%2591%258a%25e6%2589%25b9%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%2594%25a8%25e9%2581%258e%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%258a%259b-%25e6%2596%25a5%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2584%2585%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25ac%258a%25e9%25ab%2594%25e7%25b3%25bb&h=1c10c130\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200115/s00001/1579053213592/%e4%ba%ba%e6%ac%8a%e8%a7%80%e5%af%9f%e5%b9%b4%e5%ba%a6%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a%e6%89%b9%e6%b8%af%e8%ad%a6%e7%94%a8%e9%81%8e%e5%ba%a6%e6%ad%a6%e5%8a%9b-%e6%96%a5%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%a8%81%e8%84%85%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e4%ba%ba%e6%ac%8a%e9%ab%94%e7%b3%bb</a>"},{"pid":"f4bd4677ca4731df7996655087031295b253a7e9","tid":1825005,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:23:59.000Z","msg":"唔比人黎香港發布 轉去un仲大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b981c7b65106607a4efb8d6dac6f66853dfbc1","tid":1825005,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"聯合國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bd285b7f86937bfd40a50164ce4f629390d54d","tid":1825005,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"支那人其實係世界毒瘤<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSry for 少少極端，但係我覺得咁樣先係保存現代化（人類文明果實）嘅唯一方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}